FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  1 AND t.production_year  >  1983 AND ci.person_id  >  1931514 AND ci.role_id  >  1 AND mk.keyword_id  <  36078
